to go to the restroom.

1269
01:15:32,486 --> 01:15:37,950
So I had a pair of running shoes
on my feet and I had a catheter bag.

1270
01:15:38,033 --> 01:15:41,203
A doctor had come over
at about six o'clock that morning

1271
01:15:41,328 --> 01:15:44,998
and inserted a catheter so that
I'd be able to make it through the day.

1272
01:15:46,208 --> 01:15:48,460
Senator Wendy Davis must make it
to midnight.

1273
01:15:48,544 --> 01:15:50,462
That is the end of the special session.

1274
01:15:50,671 --> 01:15:53,590
Essentially she's wasting time,
running out the clock.

1275
01:15:53,674 --> 01:15:57,219
The way she's doing that? Right now,
she's reading letters from Texas women

1276
01:15:57,511 --> 01:15:59,388
who oppose this legislation.

1277
01:15:59,930 --> 01:16:02,558
...in order for their voices to be heard.

