1279
01:16:06,853 --> 01:16:08,522
Not only was she a woman

1280
01:16:08,647 --> 01:16:12,234
opposing the bill, but she was one
of the only women in the room.

1281
01:16:12,693 --> 01:16:15,112
It was an internet moment. People had left their kids
with their neighbors

1282
01:16:23,829 --> 01:16:25,789
and driven hours to Austin to be there.

1283
01:16:26,331 --> 01:16:28,542
Students had left their college campuses

1284
01:16:28,625 --> 01:16:31,253
and came to Austin
to hear Wendy filibuster.

1285
01:16:31,962 --> 01:16:34,339
These are Texans who relied
on the minority...

1286
01:16:34,423 --> 01:16:35,799
I'm a Texan.

1287
01:16:35,882 --> 01:16:39,094
Never seen the outpouring of activism
like we saw there.

1288
01:16:39,469 --> 01:16:41,722
You literally could not get
in the capitol.

1289
01:16:41,888 --> 01:16:44,558
Every annex was full, every room was full.

1290
01:16:45,475 --> 01:16:46,518
It was extraordinary.

1291
01:16:46,810 --> 01:16:49,646
...another ruling she made
was if there was a...

